The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to label topics, which are common themes in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of neural embeddings is also a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
